## Single Source of Truth

> **Hierarchical TODO System** — Two levels:
>
> 1. **`docs/PROJECT_TODO.md`** (index): Phase Dashboard, Current Focus, Milestones, Work Log
> 2. **`docs/phases/{PHASE_PREFIX}.{N}_{NAME}.md`** (detail): Granular task checkboxes, progress per section
>
> Session start: read BOTH the index AND the active phase file.
> Task status: update the phase file, then update index dashboard.
> Work logging: add entry to index Work Log.
> All updates require user confirmation.

